Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.02,0:02:00.17,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}夏風的指引  帶來變革的風暴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.82,0:02:04.86,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}將波長同步
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.32,0:02:10.32,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}如同浪漫故事般  善解人意的話語
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.53,0:02:12.88,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}也無處可尋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.22,0:02:19.42,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}只能以藍天為目標
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.63,0:02:24.26,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}如此我們就能合而為一
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.52,0:02:29.62,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}無論是迷茫的淚水  還是夢想
